ents with a history of seizures or other risk factors for seizures (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/288713/', '', 'Ephedrine, Phentermine, Orlistat, Lorcaserin, Diethylpropion, Mazindol, Viloxazine', '', 1767369485);
