enerally be avoided unless alternative treatment options are inadequate.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/288715/', '', 'Nitrazepam, Zopiclone, Dichloralphenazone', '', 1767369485);
